\pard\f0\fs28 Rhizomatous perennials with leafy stems. Leaves sessile, amplexicaul. Inflorescence a terminal raceme. Flowers small, white. Perianth-segments 6, patent, stellate, free or connate only at the base. Stamens introrse, inserted at the base of the perianth. Ovary 3-locular with 2 ovules in each loculus. Fruit a berry; seeds 1-2.
